            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add approx. 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span>&nbsp;of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> (that your lasagne sheets are cooking in) to the <strong>mince</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped&nbsp;mushrooms</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cook for a further 5 min or until the mushrooms are tender and the sauce has thickened</p>\r\n<p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> &ndash;&nbsp;this is your<strong> ragu</strong></p>",
